WEBVTT

00:02:57.827 --> 00:03:01.567
including Australia,
Canada and the United States.

00:03:01.591 --> 00:03:06.095
We may soon see a similar
explosion of cases in these countries.

00:03:07.393 --> 00:03:10.398
And while we think that HIV is done

00:03:10.422 --> 00:03:12.420
and that the tide has turned for it,

00:03:12.444 --> 00:03:15.410
just like with real tides,
it can come right back.

00:03:15.834 --> 00:03:19.270
In the early 1960s,
malaria was on the ropes.

00:03:19.294 --> 00:03:21.289
As the number of cases dropped,

00:03:21.313 --> 00:03:24.082
people and governments
stopped paying attention.

00:03:24.106 --> 00:03:28.860
The result was a deadly resurgence
of drug-resistant malaria.

00:03:29.562 --> 00:03:31.250
